=== Rashes and Skin Manifestations
<subsec:rashes>

*Clinical Presentation.*

    - Urticaria (hives)
    - Flushing and redness
    - Eczema or atopic dermatitis
    - Unexplained rashes
    - Livedo reticularis (mottled skin discoloration)
    - Pallor or grayish skin tone
